      "content": "i'm kinda dreading going to the doctor though lol, u know how expensive it is here in vancouver and the wait times are insane. i really don't think it's broken, it just feels like a really bad sprain. if i just take some ibuprofen and keep it iced and elevated, how long should i give it before i actually worry about something serious?",
